OL,5,G0156 Off Air
OL,6,G0725 Heartbeat
OL,7,     FA tragic story about an outbreak
OL,8,     Fof foot and mouth disease in a
OL,9,     Fremote farm. Reg Manston has built
OL,10,     Fup his pedigree herd through years
OL,11,     Fof work and now has to face losing
OL,12,     Fit all.
OL,13,G0825 A Touch Of Frost
OL,14,     FThere are two horrific murders for
OL,15,     FFrost to solve, and both cases
OL,16,     Fmake as many demands on the man's
OL,17,     Fcompassion as on his professional
OL,18,     Fexpertise.
OL,19,G1035 Hairy Bikers Go West
OL,20,     FThe boys reunite to travel down
OL,21,     Fthe west coast of the UK, starting
OL,22,     Fin Scotland and ending in Devon.
